        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M9 15l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        Certificados de Salud
      </a></li>
